Content:
Come Again is the debut album by Canadian rock band Thornley. This followed the 2002 break up of frontman Ian Thornley's previous group, Big Wreck. Singles off the album include "So Far So Good", "Easy Comes", "Come Again" and "Beautiful". All of which found considerable radio airplay upon release. 2007 [Special Edition] Album 
